com.hypernovalabs.multichoiceform.form

Class MCFTextInputStep

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hypernovalabs.multichoiceform.form.MCFStep
      • com.hypernovalabs.multichoiceform.form.MCFTextInputStep

  • public class MCFTextInputStep
extends MCFStep
    Created by ldemorais on 5/23/18. ldemorais@hypernovalabs.com

    Provides a new activity with a single TextInputLayout and an optional explanatory text. Also performs a Regex validation on the TextInputEditText if required.
